OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774379485
OL,3,CVictim named as pair charged in
OL,4,Cconnection with murder investigation
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "Orinta's family
OL,7,Fhave been informed and have asked for
OL,8,Fprivacy at this time. They are being
OL,9,Fsupported by specially-trained
OL,10,Fofficers."
OL,12,FA 64-year-old man and 60-year-old
OL,13,Fwoman were also arrested but have
OL,14,Fsince been released without charge.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Matt Scott said:
OL,17,F"Our thoughts are with Orinta's loved
OL,18,Fones at this incredibly difficult time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
