PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1774379485
OL,3,CVictim named as pair charged in
OL,4,Cconnection with murder investigation
OL,6,F"Police and crime scene officers have
OL,7,Fbeen working tirelessly to establish
OL,8,Fthe circumstances of this tragic
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,F"Specially-trained officers are
OL,12,Fcontinuing to support Orinta's family
OL,13,Fand keep them updated as the
OL,14,Finvestigation progresses.
OL,16,F"We have now charged two suspects as
OL,17,Fpart of our investigation but our
OL,18,Finquiries are still ongoing, so we'd
OL,19,Fask anyone who has any information but
OL,20,Fhasn't shared it with us yet to please
OL,21,Fdo so immediately."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
